What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this course to other students because it is such an experience. If you are used to using a regular 35 mm camera, you will find this course refreshingly different. If you don't want to have to deal with lugging a large camera around though then this class may not be for you.
